race.description: Heritage Bro's Funeral Services Tweed Coast Hcp
race.comment: Plenty of these come here in-form which makes it tough. Going with the sparingly raced mare HOT WINGS (4) who returned from a ten-month spell with an authoritative all-the-way win over this course and distance 17 days ago. Tackles the boys this time but with some natural improvement under a similar weight she can get the job done again. STATEMENT OF TRUTH (7) is back after a 16-week absence. Opened last prep with a placing at the Gold Coast then went on to be competitive in Brisbane Saturday company. Two recent trials will have him ready for this. VORKUTA (8) led but was nailed right on the line last time out over this course and distance. Should go forward again and give backers a sight. MUSIC FEVER (16) was no match for HOT WINGS last time but does get a weight swing today. Good each-way hope. MATERIALIST (5) finished third when resuming in the HOT WINGS race last start and has great scope for improvement.
